        <Parent_String>dissection puzzles [300222280], put-together puzzles [300222282], mechanical puzzles [300222284], puzzles (recreational artifacts) [300211207], recreational artifacts (equipment) [300218781], Recreational Artifacts (hierarchy name) [300136012], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
